{"tid":912843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】G20前又出招 傳美國尋求盟友封殺華為 向棄用華為國家提供財務援助","createTime":"2018-11-23T03:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T17:50:05.000Z","uid":35790,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bba7b412d72591b08d3e0580b7b49bc2cb684f06","tid":912843,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:38:24.000Z","msg":"【貿易戰】G20前又出招 傳美尋求盟友封殺華為<br />\n <br />\nG20將月底展開，習近平特朗普會晤在即，外媒指美國正要求盟友棄用華為作通訊及網絡設備供應商。<br />\n<br />\n據《華盛頓郵報》引述知情人士指出，美國官員已向包括德國、意大利及日本等國家，指出採用華為設備的網絡安全風險。這些國家已廣泛採用華為設備。據悉美國更考慮採用銀彈戰術，向棄用華為的國家提供財務援助。<br />\n<br />\n這些國家都設有美軍基地，是為美國憂慮之一。雖然國防部有獨立網絡傳送敏感訊息，但軍事通訊大都是經商用網絡。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"3298243a0f1be3eb04c8ed97f543f1a7fc1a8a94","tid":912843,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490f155811e5050262242d664a94135cfd4bdab8","tid":912843,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:44:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb57ced75a6b3c648b367ec3b3d365e4a47fe96","tid":912843,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a54edec5c92d4fa89c3f915c418867d285ed462","tid":912843,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0f41f90a0afa47d3a14f478604883998266ba2","tid":912843,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:43:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c946191fb58b47f8b4fba6ae1a60d2d4053886db","tid":912843,"uid":76470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:44:10.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo